modName: Queenieangels High Elves Avarantha and Avathandal Aman
summary: Those are the High Elves Avarantha and Avathandal Aman, with 7Base, 7Base TBBP HDT, ADEC, ADEC TBBP, CBBE, CBBE TBBP,  UNPB, and UNPB BBP Body. For him Better Males Body by Chris57 and FavoredSoul.
descriptionHtml:
[size=3]

[/size][img]https://i.imgur.com/2yFYLXt.jpg[/img]
[font=Georgia][color=#38761D][size=4][i]Those are the Highelfs Avarantha and Avathandal Aman, with 7Base, 7Base TBBP
HDT, ADEC, ADEC TBBP, CBBE, CBBE TBBP, UNPB, and UNPB BBP Body. For him
Better Males Body by Chris57 and FavoredSoul[/i][/size][/color][/font]

[font=Georgia][color=#6aa84f][size=4][i]After several request from a user, i've been thinking of, to offering both Elves![/i][/size][/color][/font]

[font=Georgia][color=#38761D][size=4][i]This is a Standalone Mod[/i][/size][/color][/font]

[font=Georgia][color=#b6d7a8][size=4][i]Location:[/i][/size][/color][/font]
[font=Georgia][color=#6aa84f][size=3][i]Avarantha-Highelf EnClassThalmorWizard /Levl.30. Avathandal-CombatWarrior 2
Handed/Levl.40: You find both in Ivarstead, VilemyrInn.[/i][/size][/color][/font]
[img]https://i.imgur.com/gLQaQ3t.jpg[/img]
[img]https://i.imgur.com/NVRfN1F.jpg[/img]
[img]https://i.imgur.com/RPQtbMf.jpg[/img]

[font=Georgia][color=#38761D][size=4][i]Recommend:[/i][/size][/color][/font]
[font=Georgia][color=#93c47d][size=3][i]-For All BBP_TBBP Versions: These body options do have extra requirements refer to those mod pages if you need extra help
-NOTE: To run any BBP/TBBP-Body version Mod properly, you have to install a
skeleton which supports BBP or TBBP such as XP32's XP32 Maximum
Skeleton, which is what i have used. If not you'll get a crash at
startup.
There are several skeleton/animation/package options out there to choose from.[/i][/size][/color][/font]
[font=Georgia][color=#38761D][size=3][i]
YOU NEED THIS OR ELSE YOU WILL CRASH TO THE DESKTOP!!![/i][/size][/color][/font]

[font=Georgia][color=#b6d7a8][size=3][i]Does not replace anything in Game!![/i][/size][/color][/font]
